title: Los Matematicos - Gogo En Rojo EP Vinyl Rip vintage 60s spanish
description:
A Spanish speaking rock band in the 60s called Los Matematicos. I think they were from Argentina if I remember correctly... not 100% on that. Their short "GoGo En Rojo" EP is catchy, has a few Spanish originals, then also two Kinks covers- All Day and all of the night & You really got me - which are also sung in Spanish. Then there is one instrumental that is really groovy. enjoy!
